    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through the entire RPM range via individual throttle bodies. The chassis remains composed thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, addressing the platform's primary structural concerns. It utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission with crisp gate engagement and a factory-spec limited-slip differential for precise torque vectoring. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates within tight tolerances. While exhibiting minor cosmetic patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are exceptionally sharp, offering a visceral, analog driving experience.",
