      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-strung S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine paired with a row-your-own 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The engine exhibits strong compression across all cylinders, with the critical dual-VANOS system recently serviced and the rod bearings addressed for long-term reliability. The chassis remains composed thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed polyurethane bushings, while the Variable M Differential Lock provides predictable power delivery under lateral load. It retains its factory-spec individual throttle bodies and tuned exhaust manifold, delivering a visceral induction note and linear power delivery to the 8,000 RPM redline. While the finish shows light road wear, the mechanical fundamentals are dialed in for the enthusiast who prioritizes turn-in response and drivetrain integrity.",
